cu.explanation_en: Setting Asn1_verbosity to an invalid enum value 'invalid' will cause configuration parsing errors and prevent the CU from starting properly.

du.explanation_en: Setting rfsimulator modelname to an invalid enum value 'invalid' will cause configuration parsing errors and prevent the DU from starting properly.
du.explanation_zh: 將 rfsimulator modelname 設定為無效的枚舉值 'invalid' 會導致配置解析錯誤，並阻止 DU 正確啟動。
